		<Item class="ModuleScript" referent="RBX28F1BACD520C487CA3373F538F908840">
			<Properties>
				<Content name="LinkedSource"><null></null></Content>
				<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[--[[

Forked from CmdUtl v5 by Anaminus.
Maintained by Fractality.
Logo by StuntDesigner.

Changelog:
	19/3/16
		* History waypoints are now created before anchor operation
		* Rotation works properly when the increment modulo pi is nonzero
		* Rotation indicator is agnostic to rotation direction
		* Deselect callbacks no longer create history waypoints
		* Performance improvements for the Resize tool
		* Resize, Move, and Rotate tools only recompute state when it makes sense for them to do so
	26/3/16
		* Reworked how meshes are handled with the Scale tool
		* Scale tool now uses BlockMeshes for block parts
	6/5/16
		* Somewhat improved the accessibility of the macro configs (still dismal)
		* Extinguished remaining references to FormFactor
		* Made rotation increment snapping math more robust
		* Reduced memory usage by freeing up the reference to the initializer function after it loads
		* Resources are now fetched explicitly over HTTPS (improves compatibility with gametest builds)
		* Menu activation button is highlighted when the menu is activated
		* Added a keybinding for SelectEdge
		* Added ResizeWorld tool
	14/6/16
		* Added support for new BasePart properties
	10/7/16
		* Part resizing is 40x faster for parts in close proximity to other parts
		* Stability fixes for the scaling tool
	25/7/16
		* Don't anchor parts while transforming unless the game is running
		* Selections are more efficient
		* Fixed resizing performance issues again
	27/7/16
		* Fixed SelectEdge mouse behavior
		* Fixed RotatePivot mouse behavior
		* Fixed MoveFirst mouse behavior
		* Removed most dependencies on the Mouse (the selector is still a holdout)
		* SelectEdge uses mousebutton3
	
--]]]]></ProtectedString>
				<string name="ScriptGuid">{37BA8B13-F47C-445F-A86E-5328118B8519}</string>
				<BinaryString name="AttributesSerialize"></BinaryString>
				<SecurityCapabilities name="Capabilities">0</SecurityCapabilities>
				<bool name="DefinesCapabilities">false</bool>
				<string name="Name">readme</string>
				<int64 name="SourceAssetId">-1</int64>
				<BinaryString name="Tags"></BinaryString>
			</Properties>
		</Item>
	</Item>
</roblox>